edu.snu.onyx.compiler.optimizer.pass.compiletime.reshaping

Class SailfishCodecReshapingPass

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.onyx.compiler.optimizer.pass.compiletime.reshaping.ReshapingPass
      • edu.snu.onyx.compiler.optimizer.pass.compiletime.reshaping.SailfishCodecReshapingPass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompileTimePass, Serializable, Function<DAG<IRVertex,IREdge>,DAG<IRVertex,IREdge>>

    public final class SailfishCodecReshapingPass
extends ReshapingPass
    Pass to modify the DAG for a job to batch the disk seek. It adds two OperatorVertexs with SailfishEncodingTransform and SailfishDecodingTransform before and after the shuffle edges, to enable the relaying vertex to receive and send data in arrays of bytes. If the DAG before this pass like below: Map -(SG)- Reduce The DAG will be processed like: Map -(O2O)- SailfishEncoding -(Shuffle)- SailfishDecoding -(O2O)- Reduce
